<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/335784-i-m-torn-about-reading-this-because-i">I&#39;m torn about reading this because I pretty much always like the book better than the movie. And in this case, I am such a huge fan of the movie I couldn&#39;t bear for the book to ruin it for me! Help?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_335784'><a id="like_count_community_question_335784" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/335784?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">32 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F21787.The_Princess_Bride">like</a></span>

